*Plašim* se da ću biti kažnjen. (I'm afraid I'll be punished.)

*Plašim* se od oluje. (I'm afraid of the storm.)

Nisam se *plašio* da priznam istinu. (I wasn't afraid to confess the truth.)

Životinje su se *plašile*. (The animals were afraid.)

Moje dete se *plaši* svega. (My child is afraid of everything.)